  02 May 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> mate-control-center-1.6.2.ebuild,
  mate-control-center-1.8.1.ebuild:
  Remove libappindicator dependency, fixes bug #509278; restrict mate-desktop
  dependency to 1.6 for mate-control-center 1.6, due to build failure.

*mate-control-center-1.8.1 (28 Apr 2014)

  28 Apr 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org>
