  Version bump to 1.8.1.

  24 Mar 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> mate-control-center-1.6.2.ebuild:
  SLOT move from 2 to 0.

  24 Mar 2014; Tom Wijsman <TomWij@gentoo.org> mate-control-center-1.6.2.ebuild:
  Temporarily fix parallel build issue with -j1, discovered while building all
  MATE packages at once.

